      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ATTENTION SEEKER (5) is worth forgiving last start after finishing fifth (23.01) from Box 1 at Gawler over 400m. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with three wins from five starts. Rates on top in this line up. WEBLEC STELLA (7) turned in a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 530m behind Sinaloa Bandit (31.46) in a Special conditions race. Was in the money the start prior. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Bold showing expected. BIG BOSS GIBLET (4) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish half a length away in second (30.83) behind City Of Love at this track. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Expected to feature again. DASHING NANDO (1) is another with top-three prospects.",
